                    </div>
                    <span>This is the kind of reference book that would have made those boring college courses more than bearable. And its quirky "take" on American pop culture serves as a useful complement to Ken Burns, "American Experience" and "Antiques Roadshow." Are you listening, PBS?</span>
                  
              
